# <type>(<scope>): <description>   — single line, ≤72 chars, no body
#
# type:  feat fix docs style refactor perf test build ci chore revert
# scope: optional, lowercase  (e.g. home, components, domain, hooks)
# rules: lowercase except proper nouns; imperative mood; no trailing period
#
# Split unrelated changes into separate commits. Bypass hooks with --no-verify.
